      <description>&lt;p&gt;Throughout my career, I have created several iOS app icons. The biggest challenge is to express the idea of the app through simple graphics. At the same time, the icon should be unique and attractive.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Some of the icons have been A/B tested to find the best performing versions.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://apps.apple.com/us/app/locader-changing-wallpaper-based-on-location/id1061791495?mt=12&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;./images/image0.webp&#34; alt=&#34;&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;ios-app-icons-i-made&#34;&gt;iOS App Icons I Made&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;image-grid&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &#xA;  &#xA;  &#xA;  &#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;grid-item&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &#xA;        &lt;img src=&#34;./images/image01.webp&#34; alt=&#34;Grid image 1&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;grid-item&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &#xA;        &lt;img src=&#34;./images/image02.webp&#34; alt=&#34;Grid image 2&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;      &#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;grid-item&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &#xA;        &lt;a href=&#34;https://apps.apple.com/us/app/gps-navigation-hiking-compass/id791684332&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener noreferrer&#34;&gt;&#xA;          &lt;img src=&#34;./images/image03.webp&#34; alt=&#34;Grid image 3&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;      &#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;grid-item&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &#xA;        &lt;img src=&#34;./images/image04.webp&#34; alt=&#34;Grid image 4&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;      &#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;grid-item&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &#