d {&#xA;    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);  &#xA;  }&#xA;}&#xA;&lt;/style&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;macos-app-icons-i-made&#34;&gt;macOS App Icons I Made&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;image-grid&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &#xA;  &#xA;  &#xA;  &#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;      &#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;grid-item&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &#xA;        &lt;a href=&#34;https://apps.apple.com/us/app/locader-changing-wallpaper-based-on-location/id1061791495?mt=12&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener noreferrer&#34;&gt;&#xA;          &lt;img src=&#34;./images/image10.webp&#34; alt=&#34;Grid image 1&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;      &#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;      &#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;grid-item&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &#xA;        &lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/posts/blog/2024/waterlogue-pro-macos-app-icon-creation/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener noreferrer&#34;&gt;&#xA;          &lt;img src=&#34;./images/image20.webp&#34; alt=&#34;Grid image 2&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;      &#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;grid-item&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &#xA;        &lt;img src=&#34;./images/image21.webp&#34; alt=&#34;Grid image 3&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;style&gt;&#xA;.image-grid {&#xA;  display: grid;&#xA;  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);  &#xA;  gap: 5px;&#xA;  width: 100%;&#xA;  margin: 0 auto;&#xA;  padding: 20px 0;&#xA;}&#xA;&#xA;.grid-item {&#xA;  width: 100%;&#xA;  justify-content: center;&#xA;  display: flex;&#xA;  aspect-ratio: 1/1;&#xA;  background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);&#xA;  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);&#xA;  border-radius: 10px;&#xA;}&#xA;&#xA;@media (prefers-color-scheme: dark){&#xA;  .grid-item {&#xA;    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);&#xA;    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);&#xA;  }&#xA;}&#xA;&#xA;.grid-item img,&#xA;.grid-item a {&#xA;  width: 100%;&#xA;  max-width: 120px;&#xA;  height: auto;&#xA;  object-fit: cover;&#xA;  display: block;&#xA;  margin: auto;&#xA;  justify-content: center;&#xA;  align-self: center;&#xA;  transition: transform 0.2s;&#xA;}&#xA;&#xA;.grid-item a:hover img{&#xA;  transform: scale(1.1);&#xA;}&#xA;&#xA; &#xA;@media (max-width: 768px) {&#xA;  .image-grid {&#xA;    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);  &#xA;  }&#xA;}&#xA;&lt;/style&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Many of them can be found in Michael Flarup&amp;rsquo;s &lt;a href=&#34;https://x.com/flarup/status/1567433631626395649/video/1&#34;&gt;The iOS App Icon Book&lt;/a&gt; as well. Learn process behind the app icons making process in the &lt;a href=&#34;https://interfacecraft.online/posts/blog/2024/waterlogue-pro-macos-app-icon-creation/&#34;&gt;Waterlogue Pro app icon&lt;/a&gt; case.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
